title: Board records
context: §442-16 Board records. The board shall keep for public inspection a record of all licenses issued containing: the name, license number, effective and expiration dates of the license, and status of the license of the person to whom the license to practice chiropractic is issued. [L 1925, c 99, §11; RL 1935, §969; RL 1945, §2080; RL 1955, §60-11; am L Sp 1959 2d, c 1, §19; HRS §442-16; am L 1969, c 48, §6; am L 1992, c 150, §7]
